Insider Activity


Individual




Bruce Christopher Kirchhoff



Mr. Bruce C. Kirchhoff is Secretary, Vice President & General Counsel at Royal Gold, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Rocky Mountain Mineral Law Foundation.
Mr. Kirchhoff was previously employed as Partner by Carver Kirchhoff Schwarz McNab & Bailey LLC, Partner by Carver & Kirchhoff LLC, Partner by Alfers & Carver LLC, and Senior Attorney by Cyprus AMAX Minerals Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from Colorado College, a graduate degree from the University of Denver, and a graduate degree from the Colorado School of Mines.



