Bruce Christopher Kirchhoff

Age : 58Public asset : 4,589,908 USDLinked companies :  Royal Gold, Inc (USA) 





Summary 



Mr. Bruce C. Kirchhoff is Secretary, Vice President & General Counsel at Royal Gold, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Rocky Mountain Mineral Law Foundation.Mr. Kirchhoff was previously employed as Partner by Carver Kirchhoff Schwarz McNab & Bailey LLC, Partner by Carver & Kirchhoff LLC, Partner by Alfers & Carver LLC, and Senior Attorney by Cyprus AMAX Minerals Co.He received his undergraduate degree from Colorado College, a graduate degree from the University of Denver, and a graduate degree from the Colorado School of Mines.



