Christopher M. T. Thompson

Age : 69Public asset : 3,414,830 USDLinked companies :  Jacobs Engineering Group Inc -  Royal Gold, Inc (USA) 





Summary 



Mr. Christopher M. Thompson is on the Board of Directors at Royal Gold, Inc., Jacobs Engineering Group, Inc., GeoSynFuels LLC, Teck Metals Ltd. and Colorado School of Mines Foundation, Inc. Mr. Thompson was previously employed as an Independent Director by Golden Star Resources Ltd., Chairman by Ram Power Corp., an Independent Director by Teck Resources Ltd., Chairman by World Gold Council Ltd., Chairman by Gold Fields Ltd., and President & Chief Executive Officer by The Castle Group, Inc.He also served on the board at Frontera Copper Corp.He received his graduate degree from the University of Bradford and a graduate degree from Rhodes University.



